msgid ""
"If \"Use additional script\" is selected in the AP Group tab, the following "
"content will be treated as a shell script and executed before each defined "
"Wi-Fi is created. You can use the following variables: <b>$_ENABLED</b>, "
"<b>$_SSID</b>, <b>$_BAND</b>, <b>$_NETWORK</b>. These variables will be "
"replaced with the appropriate values from the Wi-Fi. <b>Verify script before "
"saving and using!</b>"
msgstr ""
"如果在 AP 组选项卡中选择了“使用附加脚本”，则以下内容将被视为 shell 脚本，"
"并在创建每个定义的 Wi-Fi 之前执行。您可以使用以下变量：<b>$_ENABLED</b>、"
"<b>$_SSID</b>、<b>$_BAND</b>、<b>$_NETWORK</b>。这些变量将被替换为 Wi-Fi 的"
"相应值。<b>在保存和使用前请验证脚本！</b>"

